profile: Trusted by home buyers for more then 15 years to help them make informed buying decisions. For a limited time we are offering Thermal Imaging with every inspection.  Our inspectors are certified and carry full insurance.  We are the #1 rated inspectors in the Hamilton - Niagara Region.  We continue to win numerous awards in the home inspection category which most recently include; 2021 Consumer Choice Award - Hamilton - Niagara, 2020 Hamilton Spectator Readers Choice award, 2020 Niagara Falls Review Platinum Award and the 2018 CHCH Business Excellence Award.  We have an overall combined google and Homestars rating of 98% which is tops in our category as well.
services: Home Inspections, P.D.I. Inspections, 1 year warranty Inspections, Septic Inspections, W.E.T.T. Inspections, Asbestos & Mould testing, Indoor Air Quality testing
